{"tid":1432853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[民間記者會] 千祈唔好 cut 街坊分享時間同度講稿!!!","createTime":"2019-08-08T10:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T17:33:59.000Z","uid":182291,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6bb6e72f74b7bfe72aac729b0c8e5dd15b49807d","tid":1432853,"uid":182291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:38:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果要cut, 就 cut 人數! 千祈唔好cut 街坊分享時間! 更加唔好度定講稿俾佢地講!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">街坊分享最重要係咩? </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真情流露</span></span>。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">明眼人一眼就可以睇出黎<span style=\"color: red;\">街坊係跟稿讀，定真心話</span>。限分享時間亦會令到街坊有壓力，心底話要好多慢慢講先講到出黎，尤其係老人家，所以唔好cut 分享時間，唔好度講稿! 我個人覺得如果分享時間太長的話，兩三個街坊已經好足夠，少啲街坊分享記者會都可以 focus 啲。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家點睇?</span>"},{"pid":"a115f1ee22c7e712b00b136e4f1c70660f36ae6b","tid":1432853,"uid":182291,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:53:42.000Z","msg":"另外覺得最後可以多謝下上黎分享嘅街坊手足？始終佢地都要好有勇氣先上到黎<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"0ca943e7eb12fa92e0da72d29b12c937c219452e","tid":1432853,"uid":160601,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:15:49.000Z","msg":"其中有個係我親人<br />\n我驚過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e4e5101867139b29daf3e802836cacdcebb692","tid":1432853,"uid":182291,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0ca943e7eb12fa92e0da72d29b12c937c219452e","tid":1432853,"uid":160601,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:15:49.000Z","msg":"其中有個係我親人<br />\n我驚過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class